reviewText: This tape is actually just the music-only, no-narration version of the tape "Tornadoes!! The Entity" which I already had, so not really what I was hoping for, but still has some awesome and hard-to-find pre-2000s tornado footage. Audio was a little faint though
when I first watched it, simitar logo came on, then the main feature. at the end of the tape, it was halfway done. not happy about this. do not buy if you like the history channel.
